{
  "title": "Dense Crispy Japanese White Yam Gyoza",
  "description": "A delicious and crispy Japanese dumpling dish made with white yams, shio-cure, and a variety of spices. Perfect for adventurous foodies looking for a umami-packed snack.",
  "cuisine": "Japanese",
  "diet": [
    "vegetarian",
